{"tid":487560,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去東歐 跟團定自由行好?","createTime":"2017-12-02T23:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T13:45:24.000Z","uid":72478,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"36e4da5986567f8e0283cfcf28c3be8e60136c84","tid":487560,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T23:58:21.000Z","msg":"今日見到啲旅行社東歐團 7200蚊8日 <br />\n單人房加2000 者係9200蚊8日<br />\n 但得8日好似唔多夠玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋未試過跟團 唔知道有咩好處同壞處<br />\n<br />\n如果自由行既話就想玩十幾日 <br />\n但啲人話就無跟團咁平<br />\n其實旨在行下睇下景<br />\n如果窮玩 唔食貴野 訓普通酒店/青旅<br />\n純去睇景睇教堂  <br />\n希望15000蚊搞店會唔會有啲難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5aab198f24459ff8e1d527b76f85e3cac90aaf","tid":487560,"uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:27:16.000Z","msg":"跟團啦<br />\n<br />\n咁你都問得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4adf75a08ce6d4229dc810f02cc165671359e4","tid":487560,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:30:51.000Z","msg":"自己去就自由行啦！<br />\n除非你同屋企人去姐"},{"pid":"cac65ab497cf2512e197dd0d98d65de7bef3b7a1","tid":487560,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T01:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟團啦<br />\n<br />\n咁你都問得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不能同意更多"},{"pid":"be60bedf856e7c774471bfd50f26ba8df3ab727d","tid":487560,"uid":89240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:45:05.000Z","msg":"幾多歲"},{"pid":"b54cd4e6e8743e400a70952b4faa7010e248ef41","tid":487560,"uid":1482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"去到報local tour好過啦"},{"pid":"5d2484f8edd54f33c7107fa920c8c7fe75a0eeae","tid":487560,"uid":50391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日見到啲旅行社東歐團 7200蚊8日 <br />\n單人房加2000 者係9200蚊8日<br />\n 但得8日好似唔多夠玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋未試過跟團 唔知道有咩好處同壞處<br />\n<br />\n如果自由行既話就想玩十幾日 <br />\n但啲人話就無跟團咁平<br />\n其實旨在行下睇下景<br />\n如果窮玩 唔食貴野 訓普通酒店/青旅<br />\n純去睇景睇教堂  <br />\n希望15000蚊搞店會唔會有啲難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完全係2種玩法<br />\n<br />\n跟團你預再俾多d 貼士同可能有幾餐自費，多3千左右<br />\n<br />\n自由行自由度大，但要𠌥大好多功課<br />\n<br />\n你旨在睇下景，如果個團行程啱，咪跟團囉"},{"pid":"4c1bb5ae9ed0c0978454c868e4ec62215f90b17e","tid":487560,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"咁樣問得都係跟團啦"},{"pid":"57b9bbeb0ba0ae0deed396146042f38eff66531b","tid":487560,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樣問得都係跟團啦</blockquote><br />\n 東歐咁撚大你去晒？<br />\n旅行團又要去買野仲有幾多時間剩"},{"pid":"27a80a806f2d7a0854c065be7efa37bc0e84b525","tid":487560,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"無時間plan,本身未去過自由行<br />\n對身邊警覺性低 怕煩 可以跟團 可以唔洗用腦就可以睇到風景名勝<br />\n<br />\n自由行 要有心慢慢plan 語言水平(英文)正正常常<br />\n<br />\n如果獨遊又未試過 你去返轉日本台灣先<br />\n你覺得handle到先去東歐"},{"pid":"2fce52b5ff95480da990333848fad0a4e63c1d10","tid":487560,"uid":95237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:06:05.000Z","msg":"其實睇你有無時間plan同想咩旅行風格<br />\n只要有基本自理同英文能力 我會揀唔跟團<br />\n我第一次獨遊都係去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f240061445c274bb0df26a97fab98a5362cb6b","tid":487560,"uid":44702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日見到啲旅行社東歐團 7200蚊8日 <br />\n單人房加2000 者係9200蚊8日<br />\n 但得8日好似唔多夠玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋未試過跟團 唔知道有咩好處同壞處<br />\n<br />\n如果自由行既話就想玩十幾日 <br />\n但啲人話就無跟團咁平<br />\n其實旨在行下睇下景<br />\n如果窮玩 唔食貴野 訓普通酒店/青旅<br />\n純去睇景睇教堂  <br />\n希望15000蚊搞店會唔會有啲難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家做緊你自由行講會做既野 都係十幾日萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3f1a56a2bee4168620db7c65452accdb967136","tid":487560,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日見到啲旅行社東歐團 7200蚊8日 <br />\n單人房加2000 者係9200蚊8日<br />\n 但得8日好似唔多夠玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋未試過跟團 唔知道有咩好處同壞處<br />\n<br />\n如果自由行既話就想玩十幾日 <br />\n但啲人話就無跟團咁平<br />\n其實旨在行下睇下景<br />\n如果窮玩 唔食貴野 訓普通酒店/青旅<br />\n純去睇景睇教堂  <br />\n希望15000蚊搞店會唔會有啲難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家做緊你自由行講會做既野 都係十幾日萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求開心share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6502495c96c13b8edfdef467cad5ad622f4bd75","tid":487560,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"緊係自由行啦<br />\n又唔係文盲<br />\n驚咩<br />\n識英文就得啦"},{"pid":"cdd52a340101d90eb8748cfc4f393087644d6701","tid":487560,"uid":10039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:24:19.000Z","msg":"自由行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我4月去 50日 都係東歐個邊<br />\n要做好大堆功課係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ffd20cf7ef54ba959ab1123fa41bf44b104e05","tid":487560,"uid":46020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"如果你英文唔好就跟團啦<br />\n英文ok就自由行<br />\n彈性大，又可以平食<br />\n中意去邊就去邊"},{"pid":"52a769ca8f0e500874548f35e8845739f4e4d5eb","tid":487560,"uid":16697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T20:11:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾先跟團,限時限刻,未撚上到頂就夠鐘準備去集合,垃圾<br />\n8日去十幾個國家果隻,垃圾"},{"pid":"95156e98fb3368891f8ffbf9059f7e0323987f94","tid":487560,"uid":109435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T20:26:33.000Z","msg":"如果冇自由行經驗/同屋企人一齊去/唔想煩就跟團啦<br />\n感覺東歐配套冇西歐咁tourist-friendly，要做多啲功課，英文正常水平都未必溝通到。不過個人認為東歐治安都ok，啲人冇咁有機心又幾nice，自由行都安全既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d68f9759811c2b03898522cc6611743993ca978","tid":487560,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T23:50:51.000Z","msg":"自由行 要call g"},{"pid":"1c9ddc07f49e6bd5b0e227cf8207540e24551bf0","tid":487560,"uid":60061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T23:55:34.000Z","msg":"東歐自由行啦，仲安全過西歐"},{"pid":"a13eb786dc7d0b63871bfcaf04f9d099499ed6c8","tid":487560,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"有無人知東歐住民宿/青旅安全嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定住酒店好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}